    <j.0:comment xml:lang="en">The Commission can accept entirely 24 of the 57 amendments tabled (ie 1, 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 12, 16, 17, 18, 19, 21, 24, 25, 26, 29, 31, 34, 38, 41, 43, 44, 45 and 47), 2 amendments in part only (33 and 35 (1) second part) and 5 amendments subject to re-wording (13, 20, 28, 32 and 36) and  cannot accept the following amendments: 2, 7, 9, 10, 11, 15, 22, 27, 30, 37, 39, 40, 42, 46, 48, 51, 53, 54, 55, 56 and 57.&amp;#13;
</j.0:comment>
